  <brief_title>Assessment of Chest Compression Depth Obtained Using the Smartphone Application as an Educational Tool With New Attachment Device</brief_title>
  <official_title>Assessment of Chest Compression Depth Obtained Using the Smartphone Application as an Educational Tool With New Attachment Device</official_title>
  <sponsors>
